{"tid":2086074,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學生組織「學生動源」宣佈香港本部解散","createTime":"2020-06-30T07:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T08:02:32.000Z","uid":103207,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b17eef74ea44be9f69c7f5aa66e5d1dbbf59eb6a","tid":2086074,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:16:42.000Z","msg":"2020-06-30 HKT 15:13<br />\n分享工具 facebook twitter<br />\n學生組織「學生動源」宣佈香港本部解散，並設立外國分部，繼續推動香港獨立。<br />\n<br />\n「學生動源」在社交網站表示，召集人鍾翰林已根據組織會章停止香港地區一切事務，即日起遣散香港地區全體成員，所有組織事務將會交由海外成員繼續運作。學生動源海外成員將設立外國分部接管組織一切事務，繼續推動香港獨立，直至香港作為獨立主權國家前仍然會繼續前進。"},{"pid":"91a732aa92cc10bd8d285ac19020f76edb3c5302","tid":2086074,"uid":37817,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:29:46.000Z","msg":"做乜個個都走，真係咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8598a96a968df0b1a83bce8f5c4a0067ba9cbb7","tid":2086074,"uid":8014,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"91a732aa92cc10bd8d285ac19020f76edb3c5302","tid":2086074,"uid":37817,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:29:46.000Z","msg":"做乜個個都走，真係咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:31:23.000Z","msg":"你代佢地坐終身？"},{"pid":"b37607a9f5069a5bd50797b9b02369bf373788a7","tid":2086074,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91a732aa92cc10bd8d285ac19020f76edb3c5302","tid":2086074,"uid":37817,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:29:46.000Z","msg":"做乜個個都走，真係咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:32:05.000Z","msg":"走好過"},{"pid":"5bf87ff2058539edf9bfe0e36efd5ac1bf301c47","tid":2086074,"uid":154486,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"91a732aa92cc10bd8d285ac19020f76edb3c5302","tid":2086074,"uid":37817,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:29:46.000Z","msg":"做乜個個都走，真係咁驚<im